videos.description: Clemson takes an early 7-0 lead over Ohio State in the Sugar Bowl as Trevor Lawrence takes the snap and gets to the pylon to dive for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Lawrence dives for the pylon for Clemson TD

videos.description: Trey Sermon makes a catch to pick up a big 32-yard gain, then follows it up by taking a handoff into the end zone through Clemson defenders for a 32-yard score Ohio State score.

videos.headline: Sermon's big gain sets up first OSU score

videos.headline: Fields, Wilson connect for phenomenal 47-yard gain

videos.description: Justin Fields completes a pass to Jeremey Ruckert who makes his way into the end zone to score a 17-yard touchdown to give Ohio State a 21-14 lead over Clemson.

videos.headline: Ohio State's Ruckert makes the catch for 17-yard TD

videos.headline: Sermon stiff-arms defender for big Ohio State gain
